headline: Wall Street hails Charlie Javice conviction—but wonders how JPMorgan failed to catch young woman’s $175 million fraud
summary: Charlie Javice, who faces a prison sentence of 14 to 17.5 years, unsuccessfully sought to portray JPMorgan Chase as careless.
